#: ../src/fileinfo.ml:24
msgid "allow the synchronization of symbolic links (true/false/default)"
msgstr ""

#: ../src/fileinfo.ml:25
msgid ""
"When set to {\\tt true}, this flag causes Unison to synchronize symbolic "
"links.  When the flag is set to {\\tt false}, symbolic links will be ignored "
"during update detection.  Ordinarily, when the flag is set to {\\tt "
"default}, symbolic links are synchronized except when one of the hosts is "
"running Windows.  On a Windows client, Unison makes an attempt to detect if "
"symbolic links are supported and allowed by user privileges.  You may have "
"to get elevated privileges to create symbolic links.  When the flag is set "
"to {\\tt default} and symbolic links can't be synchronized then an error is "
"produced during update detection."
msgstr ""

