#: ../src/remote.ml:1595
msgid "force half-duplex communication with the server"
msgstr ""

#: ../src/remote.ml:1596
msgid ""
"When this flag is set to {\\tt true}, Unison network communication is forced "
"to be half duplex (the client and the server never simultaneously emit "
"data).  If you experience unstabilities with your network link, this may "
"help."
